{"data":[{"date":"09:32 17/07","title":"C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong su\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Paul Pogba lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef trong tay t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n, n\u01a1i in h\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed1 y\u00eau d\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh qua \u0111\u1eddi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap-c197-p1.html\" title=\"Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p\" type=\"Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p\"> b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p</span>, Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00f2 m\u00f2 khi lu\u00f4n c\u1ea7m tr\u00ean tay m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eadn c\u00fap v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Luzhiniki.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n, t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in h\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed1 Fassou Antoine c\u1ee7a Pogba, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111\u1eddi v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 79.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/DiLKd05XUAUMygZjpglarge.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Pogba lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n trong tay khi \u0111ang \u00f4m chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Fassou l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ed1c Guinea, sau \u0111\u00f3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi sinh s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, n\u01a1i con trai \u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia x\u1ee9 s\u1edf l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a cha, tr\u00ean t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Ph\u00e1p: &quot;\u00d4i Ch\u00faa, \u0111\u1eebng tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t con v\u00ec nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c n\u00f3i. H\u00e3y tha th\u1ee9 cho con v\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 hay bi\u1ebft v\u00e0 h\u00e3y gi\u00fap con tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd ngh\u0129&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1eb5m tr\u1ecdn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong tay, Pogba chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n mu\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y t\u1eb7ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eb9 th\u00e2n y\u00eau v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha qu\u00e1 c\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Pogba c\u0169ng ch\u1ee5p m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh khi c\u1ea7m tr\u00ean tay chi\u1ebfc \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n, m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a B\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Manchester United ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u00e0y v\u1edbi d\u00f2ng ch\u00fa th\u00edch: &quot;Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a B\u1ed1. B\u1ed1 \u01a1i c\u00e1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho b\u1ed1&quot;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba chia se tren Twitter buc hinh chup cung voi tam op chan in hinh bo.\" title=\"Pogba chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n in h\u00ecnh b\u1ed1.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Screen_Shot_20180717_at_033124.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Pogba chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n in h\u00ecnh b\u1ed1.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e1ng 3 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u1ec9 2 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u00f4ng Fassou qua \u0111\u1eddi, Pogba t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c sinh nh\u1eadt l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 79 cho b\u1ed1 ngay t\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n. Trong t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p hai cha con b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh chi\u1ebfc b\u00e1nh sinh nh\u1eadt, Pogba chia s\u1ebb: &quot;Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng b\u1ed1 th\u00e2n y\u00eau, con t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 con c\u1ee7a b\u1ed1&quot;. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, t\u00ecnh y\u00eau m\u00e0 Pogba d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ea5ng th\u00e2n sinh l\u00e0 v\u00f4 b\u1edd b\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 3 n\u0103m nay, khi ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, Pogba g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed1 n\u01a1i thi\u00ean \u0111\u00e0ng qua nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o ph\u00f4ng m\u1eb7c b\u00ean trong: &quot;Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng sinh nh\u1eadt b\u1ed1, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n b\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n d\u00f5i theo con v\u00e0 c\u00e1c anh em&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i World Cup v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, Pogba chia s\u1ebb: &quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi xung quanh \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 90 ph\u00fat ngo\u00e0i kia \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean nh\u1eefng trang s\u1eed c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea1ng danh n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c&quot;, Pogba chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi n\u00f3i truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng vi\u1ebft n\u00ean nh\u1eefng trang m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4295","checkdouble":"191415"},{"date":"09:12 17/07","title":"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi Milan l\u00e0\u2026 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-toi-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha cho r\u1eb1ng AC Milan n\u00ean xem x\u00e9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Milan trong suy tho\u00e1i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng CLB t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Italia, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2012/13 t\u1edbi nay, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ch\u1ec9 sau Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Milan ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 b\u00e1n CLB cho c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Trung Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 mua s\u1eafm r\u1ea7m r\u1ed9, Rossoneri v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-la-tich-cuc-cho-Milan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c chi ti\u00eau qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho Milan vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a UEFA. H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd b\u1ecb c\u01a1 quan quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\" title=\"bong da chau au\" type=\"bong da chau au\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span> c\u1ea5m d\u1ef1 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong v\u00f2ng 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNi\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Milan c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Serie A trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c t\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb gi\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. Bianconeri m\u1edbi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo va Kaka\" title=\"Ronaldo va Kaka\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1c quan cho Milan. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua 7 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n San Siro tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n l\u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean cho m\u00ecnh sau nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng t\u0103m t\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u00edch nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y m\u1eb7t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Juventus k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo&rdquo;, Kaka n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Omnisport. &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 cho Milan. Ngay c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;H\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y khi s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia-c176-p1.html\" title=\"Bong da y\" type=\"Bong da y\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia</span> \u0111ang d\u00e2ng cao. Cristiano Ronaldo mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia. C\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn anh \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. V\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Serie A tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191404.html\">HLV Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real-180-191352.html\">Kaka l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/de-ronaldo-ra-di-la-sai-lam-lon-nhat-trong-lich-su-cua-real-madrid-180-191345.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 Ronaldo ra \u0111i l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/roma-bao-tin-vui-cho-real-vu-thu-mon-alisson-180-191170.html\">Roma b\u00e1o tin vui cho Real v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a-176-191165.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Benzema s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf Serie A?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4294","checkdouble":"191405"},{"date":"11:16 17/07","title":"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo: Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc xung quanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e1m b\u1ecf t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u1ec9 cho m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng hoan ngh\u00eanh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi k\u00e9o d\u00e0i v\u00f4 t\u1eadn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Champions League \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u00f3i quen nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, trong \u0111\u00eam Turin \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 4 v\u1eeba qua, <em>si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus</em>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa &ldquo;xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u1ed5ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo; th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a anh <u>nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c C\u0110V t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz</u>. Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Juventus-chieu-mo-Ronaldo-Khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Bianconeri s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc phi th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhen nh\u00f3m trong \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n Allianz. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, 3 th\u00e1ng sau, h\u1ecd <strong>bi\u1ebfn m\u01a1 th\u00e0nh th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</strong>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi b\u1ecf s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia. \u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, <em>h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Ronaldo &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh 5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</em> v\u00e0 5 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Juventus-chieu-mo-Ronaldo-Khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo gi\u00e0nh v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Juventus, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 CLB n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ronaldo h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 khi <u>c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi m\u1edf ra, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Juve kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1</u>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t cho nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bianconeri c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y</span> t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t ph\u00e9p t\u00ednh: Ronaldo 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro? Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, <em>nh\u1eefng nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111ang k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1edbi v\u00f4 t\u1eadn</em>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00e0o l\u00e0 Juventus c\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u00f4ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u? Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n Ronaldo? Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n? Ronaldo c\u00f3 c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9?&nbsp; Ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Juventus s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 sao? Juventus c\u00f3 l\u00e2m v\u00e0o ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n? C\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 x\u1ea5u cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia? v.v. v\u00e0 v.v.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo roi Real mang theo nhieu danh hieu\" title=\"Ronaldo roi Real mang theo nhieu danh hieu\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Ronaldo-roi-Real-mang-theo-nhieu-danh-hieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">CR7 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKhi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn: Cho t\u1edbi <u>tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eddi Real, Ronaldo v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1</u> c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. 44 b\u00e0n sau 44 tr\u1eadn v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u01a1i r\u1ed9ng, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t &ldquo;s\u00e1t th\u1ee7&rdquo; v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng <em>Serie A l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng</em>. Nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Francesco Totti v\u00e0 Javier Zanetti c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t cho t\u1edbi tu\u1ed5i 40. Ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, Fabio Quagliarella d\u00f9 35 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 4 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Serie A m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi 19 b\u00e0n sau 35 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus chieu mo Ronaldo\" title=\"Juventus chieu mo Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 l\u00fd khi Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 t\u1eebng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n khi Juventus th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; 90 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi Gonzalo Higuain c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 28 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0ng con s\u1ed1 55 b\u00e0n sau 105 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 Higuain ghi cho Juve t\u1edbi nay l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o (trung b\u00ecnh 0,52 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 Ronaldo, Higuain, Dybala v\u00e0 Douglas Costa khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i n\u1ec3 s\u1ee3. N\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Bianconeri m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Joao Cancelo v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Emre Can.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro,...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3i g\u1ecdn tham v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Serie A, Juventus c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u1edbi Ronaldo. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i n\u00e0y 7 n\u0103m qua v\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u00edt d\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 an nh\u00e0n m\u1ed7i n\u0103m n\u00e2ng cao Scudetto v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f4i khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh. <strong>Juventus mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i vinh quang t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</strong>, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 12 n\u0103m. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2 l\u1ea7n trong 4 m\u00f9a qua nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 Barcelona v\u00e0 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tong hop: Inter Milan 2-3 Juventus (Vong 35 Serie A 2017/18)\" title=\"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Inter Milan 2-3 Juventus (V\u00f2ng 35 Serie A 2017/18)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/29/tong-hop-inter-milan-23-juventus-vong-35-serie-a-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus \u0111ang m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 Champions League sau 12 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft b\u1edfi ch\u00ednh Real v\u00e0 b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb penalty ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 do ch\u00ednh Ronaldo th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i Champions League, Juve ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb CR7 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 10 l\u1ea7n sau 7 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea5y v\u1ec1 th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng vua \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m Real Madrid, l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed3i. Real \u0111\u00e3 3 n\u0103m li\u1ec1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League (4 l\u1ea7n sau 5 n\u0103m) v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo &ndash; ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 coi nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Ronaldo-toi-Juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Juventus mang v\u1ec1 Ronaldo c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi PSG ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi Neymar. T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil mang l\u1ea1i cho PSG th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus th\u1ea5y r\u00f5. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf phi\u1ebfu cao \u0111\u1ec3 CLB m\u1edf k\u00e9t tr\u1ea3 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/juventus-ban-520-nghin-ao-dau-du-cristiano-ronaldo-con-chua-ra-mat-465-191382.html\" target=\"_blank\">l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n ra c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t</span> v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ed9t b\u00e1u v\u1eadt t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh Turin. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u1eb1m trong t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Juventus, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng sau 4 n\u0103m, CR7 th\u00f4ng qua th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rat nhieu CDV Juventus chao don su xuat hien cua Ronaldo.\" title=\"R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Juventus ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/FBL-ITA-SERIEA-JUVENTUS-RONALDO-(2).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u0110V Juventus nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a CR7</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ef1c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd: Tr\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Juventus n\u0103m qua v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 doanh thu b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Inter Milan b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1n c\u00e2n n\u00e0y thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ed5 phi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Juve \u0111ang t\u0103ng l\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng v\u00e0 &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hoan ngh\u00eanh, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee9 r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 (c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Champions League), vi\u1ec7c Juve l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng l\u00e0m (mua m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro) c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-tiet-lo-soc-ve-vu-chuyen-nhuong-toi-juventus-184-191410.html\">Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191404.html\">HLV Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mourinho-ronaldo-se-phuc-hung-bong-da-y-176-191396.html\">Mourinho: &ldquo;Ronaldo s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/hanh-dong-thu-vi-cua-ronaldo-khi-gioi-thieu-ao-dau-tai-juventus-327-191392.html\">H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ronaldo khi gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/sao-juventus-noi-gi-ve-dong-doi-tan-binh-ronaldo-176-191387.html\">Sao Juventus n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00e2n binh Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4293","checkdouble":"191424"},{"date":"10:40 17/07","title":"C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1eebng gi\u00fap Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/20/cong-than-tung-giup-quang-nam-vo-dich-bi-thanh-ly-hop-dong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Claudecir Junior do g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</h2><h2>CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/CLB-Quang-Nam-thanh-ly-hop-dong-voi-Claudecir-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Claudecir Junior l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u1ea1i V-League 2017, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Claudecir \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i do ch\u1ecbu \u00e1n k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt t\u1eeb CLB, Claudecir \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Qu\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 10 V-League, Claudecir c\u00f2n d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng sau pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 TP.HCM, Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00ecnh Lu\u1eadt. Theo k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129, Claudecir b\u1ecb g\u00e3y x\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e1c v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ea3ng Nam g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1i binh. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u2018\u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ai n\u1ea5y \u0111i\u2019. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00ednh Claudecir mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia tay \u2018c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n\u2019 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung t\u00e2n binh Warley Oliveira thay th\u1ebf. Ng\u00f4i sao v\u1eeba gia nh\u1eadp Qu\u1ea3ng Nam n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Brazil. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Oliveira t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i cho nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi sang ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u1eed s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u1edf\u00a0Kuwait m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft\u00a0cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Claudecir, m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 sao nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch Nguy\u1ec5n Trung \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng (Suleiman). Thay th\u1ebf anh l\u00e0 Thiago, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9c<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hai su\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1i binh l\u00e0 Douglas, Warley Oliveira c\u00f9ng su\u1ea5t nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9c (Thiago). Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 9 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng khi k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 19 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\">SLNA 2-1 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam (KT): Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng v\u00e0 Olaha, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-quang-nam-44-binh-duong-vong-18-vleague-2018-325-190702.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/tong-hop-quang-nam-44-binh-duong-vong-18-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-quang-nam-44-binh-duong-vong-18-vleague-2018-325-190702.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 4-4 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (V\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nHai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u0110inh Thanh Trung c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4292","checkdouble":"191420"},{"date":"09:37 17/07","title":"PSG mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/12/27/psg-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-danny-rose.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Tottenham, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Rose</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. HLV Thomas Tuchel \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU, PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU, PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Vuot-mat-MU,-PSG-muon-mua-Danny-Rose-cua-Tottenham-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Rose</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, PSG chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Buffon t\u1eeb Juventus theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 40 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Tuchel c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong khung g\u1ed7. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Buffon r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi PSG, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf Champions League.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Buffon, PSG t\u00ednh mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. Yuri Berchiche \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Layvin Kurzawa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Le10Sport, PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Tottenham, HLV Tuchel \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rose</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Danny Rose th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Ben Davies. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rose bi rach tai\" title=\"Rose b\u1ecb r\u00e1ch tai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/7/Mourinho-muon-MU-mua-hau-ve-Danny-Rose-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rose c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf ch\u1ed7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-don-tin-mung-tu-thuong-vu-danny-rose-172-173960.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Danny Rose</span>, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng&nbsp;Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuke Shaw \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford, Mourinho nh\u1eafm Rose nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n c\u1ed9ng Luke Shaw \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Tottenham b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi PSG th\u00ec M.U c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, ch\u1ec9 khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Rose \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, n\u1ebfu t\u1edbi PSG anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4291","checkdouble":"191408"},{"date":"09:51 17/07","title":"Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/ronaldo-tiet-lo-soc-ve-vu-chuyen-nhuong-toi-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Juventus l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a anh.</h2><h2>Ronaldo ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Juve?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn cho r\u1eb1ng anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Bernabeu sau khi Real gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Ronaldo khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Man United s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. G\u00e3 nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u PSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ti\u1ec1n \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span>. Anh ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c sau v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c sau v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/ronaldo-tiet-lo-soc-ve-vu-chuyen-nhuong-toi-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng duy nh\u1ea5t g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ra m\u1eaft h\u00f4m qua, Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Juventus l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng duy nh\u1ea5t g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho anh ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia nh\u01b0 Man United hay PSG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cL\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Juventus l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb duy nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d, Ronaldo cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cK\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf Sporting \u01b0? T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Juventus hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. T\u00f4i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Drogba \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Didier Drogba cho r\u1eb1ng Juventus l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u00f4i c\u0169ng t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid. V\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Real l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u01b0ng Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Ronaldo:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-toi-juventus-176-191405.html\">Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi Milan l\u00e0\u2026 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191404.html\">HLV Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4290","checkdouble":"191410"},{"date":"09:07 17/07","title":"HLV Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/ronaldo-tiet-lo-soc-ve-vu-chuyen-nhuong-toi-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 CR7.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf \u1edf Juventus</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus, anh nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/HLV-Julen-Lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-Cristiano-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Ronaldo&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"Bong da 24h\" type=\"Bong da 24h\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha. S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, song HLV m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 CR7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ea3. Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real v\u1eabn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Ronaldo trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec tham v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i tin Real \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Lopetegui ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u00f4ng s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real, t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 1991. \u00d4ng tin r\u1eb1ng kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng s\u1ebd m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui ra mat CLB Hoang gia sau khi bi sa thai\" title=\"Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia sau khi b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-cau-thu-nao-sau-khi-chia-tay-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui tin r\u1eb1ng qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Los Blancos</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng HLV h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn Zidane th\u00ec r\u00f5. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Real v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Zidane th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1 cho Real trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u0169ng cho t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4289","checkdouble":"191404"},{"date":"09:38 17/07","title":"V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV tai ti\u1ebfng t\u1ef1 tin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/hlv-lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 th\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi CLB l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Lopetegui ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi t\u1edbi Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 5 ng\u00e0y sau khi c\u00f9ng Real Madrid gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 2017/18, Zinedine Zidane \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u, ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018, Los Blancos c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 Julen Lopetegui s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi \u0111\u00f3 Lopetegui v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang l\u00e0 HLV \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn cho Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 (RFEF) t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 51 tu\u1ed5i. Qua \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e1ng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea7u Lopetegui c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Real. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/HLV-Lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-Real-va-tu-tin-se-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lopetegui t\u1edbi Real v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real. Tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 khi ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 3 n\u0103m li\u1ec1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Zidane.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Lopetegui t\u1eebng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Real. Khi m\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ngh\u1ec1 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng t\u1eebng n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i Real Castilla. &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec n\u1eefa, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf. Tinh th\u1ea7n &ldquo;Madridismo&rdquo; l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u&rdquo;, Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1edbi trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui la HLV Real B\" title=\"Lopetegui la HLV Real B\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/Lopetegui-la-HLV-Real-B.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;B\u1edfi v\u00ec ngo\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, kh\u00ed ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Real Madrid. C\u00e1c HLV kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1edfi c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i n\u00f3. T\u00f4i tin m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, Lopetegui c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Real hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trong c\u00e1c si\u00eau sao \u0111ang n\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 c\u1ed3n nh\u01b0 Neymar, Kylian Mbappe hay Eden Hazard&hellip;<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real-180-191352.html\">Kaka l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/de-ronaldo-ra-di-la-sai-lam-lon-nhat-trong-lich-su-cua-real-madrid-180-191345.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 Ronaldo ra \u0111i l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-real-tien-rat-gan-thuong-vu-courtois-172-191318.html\">N\u00f3ng: Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic-180-191234.html\">Real Madrid h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Mateo Kovacic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real-172-191169.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4288","checkdouble":"191412"},{"date":"09:57 17/07","title":"Real Madrid c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/1/real-madrid-co-cau-tra-loi-ve-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai, t\u1edd The Telegraph tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Los Blancos.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Zidane c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u1edf Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/HLV-Lopetegui-quyet-khong-de-Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-Madrid--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Gareth Bale&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu n\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Vi\u1ec7c Bale tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gareth Bale, Mourinho \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i MU th\u00ec Tottenham v\u00e0 Bayern Munich c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Bale r\u1eddi Real l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai, t\u1edd The Telegraph tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Los Blancos.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" title=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/real-madrid-co-cau-tra-loi-ve-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Gareth Bale \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Lopetegui</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-180-191238.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bale c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Lopetegui</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Bale, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Real v\u1eeba m\u1ea5t Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao n\u1eefa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, HLV Lopetegui c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Eden Hazard \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4287","checkdouble":"191416"},{"date":"10:19 17/07","title":"HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-tri-gia-50-trieu-bang-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jorginho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n mang v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Napoli t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Maurizio-Sarri-phat-bieu-ve-Jorginho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jorginho</span>. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London, \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Napoli nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ph\u1ea3i chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Chelsea, Jorginho s\u1ebd \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 5. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft, Jorginho chia s\u1ebb: \u201cChelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf Anh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League, b\u1edfi v\u1eady khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Chelsea c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Jorginho</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri giup Chelsea mua Jorginho\" title=\"Sarri gi\u00fap Chelsea mua Jorginho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-tri-gia-50-trieu-bang-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cJorginho kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf Napoli, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi Jorginho, b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ri\u00eang\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n hi\u1ec3u h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n g\u00ec v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho CLB\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4286","checkdouble":"191417"},{"date":"10:49 17/07","title":"Chelsea chi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Eden Hazard t\u1edbi Real Madrid, The Blues c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/Cuc-nong-Chelsea-muon-mua-Anthony-Martial-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c r\u1eddi Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3 Hazard c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea lo l\u1eafng khi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u1edbi Real Madrid: \u201cB\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n duy tr\u00ec tham v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Bernabeu lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real mu\u1ed1n mua Hazard, Los Blancos ch\u1ed1t 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Ronaldo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm Martial thay Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Eden Hazard t\u1edbi Real Madrid, HLV Sarri \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge n\u1ebfu Hazard quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial se dut ao chia tay MU he nay\" title=\"Martial s\u1ebd d\u1ee9t \u00e1o chia tay MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea t\u00ednh mua Martial thay Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Martial l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n, anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-quyet-tam-lam-kho-anthony-martial-172-190682.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U \u0111ang l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 Martial</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Mourinho c\u00f2n \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c MU b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, Chelsea d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi t\u1edbi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn MU nh\u1ea3 c\u1ef1u sao Monaco. M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Martial \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale t\u1eeb Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Anh, Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi Chelsea. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4285","checkdouble":"191418"},{"date":"11:00 17/07","title":"Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/DT-Phap-tao-dang-cung-cup-vang-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i b\u00e1o tr\u00ean The Sun, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.\r\n</h2><h2><br />\r\nPogba n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0i b\u00e1o n\u00e0y ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u1eeba qua, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbp gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 Hugo Lloris \u0111ang n\u1eafm chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, nh\u01b0ng Pogba v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Les Bleus.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i vinh danh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ee9ng ra ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eeda tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p. V\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a M.U l\u00e0 Michael Carrick gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n David De Gea hay Nemanja Matic ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, Paul Pogba ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edbt m\u00e0u m\u00e8 v\u00e0 t\u00f4 v\u1ebd h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, anh ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf h\u01a1n, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tham gia nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt khi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tung ra \u0111\u00fang 2 c\u00fa s\u00fat trong b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ham &ldquo;s\u00fat b\u1eady&rdquo; trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man United.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 th\u1ebf quen thu\u1ed9c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/DT-Phap-tao-dang-cung-cup-vang-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br />\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 Rami chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n r\u1eb1ng, Pogba \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau, nh\u01b0ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ecf h\u00e1ng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed5 h\u00f4i, x\u1eafn tay \u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p &ndash; Hugo Lloris c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng, Pogba \u0111ang d\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u00ean suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd k\u00edch th\u00edch tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng gi\u1eefa 2 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018-188-191415.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018-188-191415.html\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br />\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Paul Pogba lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef trong tay t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n, n\u01a1i in h\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed1 y\u00eau d\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh qua \u0111\u1eddi c\u00e1ch...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc-421-191349.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc-421-191349.html\">C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba, cho ph\u00e9p... \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c</span><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng Rio Ferdinand, Paul Scholes hay kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 Roy Keane cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1edf m\u00e0y n\u1edf m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf sau khi c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-len-ngoi-vo-dich-pogba-va-man-trinh-dien-dap-tan-moi-chi-trich-421-191329.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/pogba-duoc-huyen-thoai-khen-ngoi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-len-ngoi-vo-dich-pogba-va-man-trinh-dien-dap-tan-moi-chi-trich-421-191329.html\">Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch: Paul Pogba v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1eadp tan m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span><br />\r\n0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng Pogba trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4284","checkdouble":"191419"},{"date":"11:25 17/07","title":"M.U chi 92 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/mu-chi-92-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c BL\u0110 M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U chi g\u1ea7n 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Ivan Perisic, c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u1ecd t\u1eebng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Inter \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, khi anh g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao Croatia c\u0169ng ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u, Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 48 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Perisic v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp theo, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Ante Rebic, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Rebic \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Eintracht Frankfurt \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Arsenal c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Rebic v\u00e0 Rakitic\" title=\"Rebic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/mu-chi-92-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Rebic v\u00e0 Rakitic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh l\u00e0 Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa, bao g\u1ed3m 1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p chia tay Anthony Martial, M.U s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Wilian, Gareth Bale &ndash; v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Ivan Perisic c\u00f9ng Ante Rebic.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Keita, Shaqiri; Man City c\u00f3 Riyad Mahrez; Arsenal s\u1edf h\u1eefu 5 t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Chelsea c\u0169ng k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Jorginho. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0y d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/DT-Phap-tao-dang-cung-cup-vang-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\">Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba</span><br>\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i b\u00e1o tr\u00ean The Sun, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-1707-172-191425.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/12/tong-hop-nhung-sieu-pham-ban-thang-cua-ronaldo-khi-con-o-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-1707-172-191425.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 17/07</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i \u1edf, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 17/07.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4283","checkdouble":"191421"}]}